{"id": 20857, "date": "1984-02-03T11:00:00", "date_gmt": "1984-02-03T19:00:00", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=20857"}, "modified": "2026-03-14T15:25:16", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-14T22:25:16", "slug": "cover-me-justin-townes-earle-glory-days", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1984/02/03/cover-me-justin-townes-earle-glory-days/", "title": {"rendered": "Justin Townes Earle: Glory Days"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>Oh man&#8230; I don&#8217;t have the words tonight.</p>\n<p>I&#8217;ve had three of Justin Townes Earle&#8217;s wonderful covers on my to-blog list for ages, just waiting for the right inspiration or mood to strike.</p>\n<p>I never for a moment thought it would take a circumstance like this, but like the man says: the days, they pass by in the wink of an eye.</p>\n<p>Rest in peace, Justin.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-mjlETFom2g?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>\u00a9 August 23, 2020</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Rest in peace, Justin Townes Earle&#8211;gone far, far too soon. </p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 68334, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_ac